WorkItem.Description:
I've developed a multi functioning browser incorporating Explorer 9, Chromium beta and apple. It seems to be functioning awesome !
I have used the personalising that is offered through Windows and the power of the search by Google with a bit of sleek apple technology thrown in for stability. I am not quite sure if this is innovation of technology I have created or the sign of newer progress to come.
Could some kind person let me know as I have done all this in less than two years with no advice or any outside help. It is fast and powerful and a pleasure to work with and I am loving it ! If honesty is the best policy in computer networking then pop me to top of that list as I have been open throughout, embracing the people along the way with positivity and encouragement to reach their full potential in the computing world.
Sharing ideas is the key !  If everyone had though of the same ideas before being individual and steadfast in your opinion that computing must operate as a multi-functioning resource to acheive the results we really require in this modern age.
A message to everone involved 'Welcome to make web and not war' is synonomous with Microsoft, taking this in it's literal sense we have a responsibility which I embrace in discovering ones self and every person must adhere with a open heart.
Ange x
